  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether blockade of the saphenous nerve can provide
      the same degree of analgesia postoperatively for ACLS as a femoral nerve block without
      resulting motor blockade enhancing shortening of hospital stay en functional outcome.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
